### 1. Create a New Person (Valid Input)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/person
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "street": "Main Street",
  "streetNumber": "123",
  "zip": "12345",
  "location": "Springfield",
  "country": "USA"
}

### 2. Create Person (Missing First Name)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/person
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "street": "Main Street",
  "streetNumber": "123",
  "zip": "12345",
  "location": "Springfield",
  "country": "USA"
}
### Expected: HTTP 400 response with message: "Name must not be null or empty"

